snippet.title: Dynasty Warriors 7 Xtreme Legends (Shin Sangoku Musou 6) (JPN) Shu Story Part 1 PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Dynasty Warriors 7 XL (Shin Sangoku Musou 6) (JPN) Shu Story #1 PC Gameplay

*I suggest you watch at 720p or 1080p*

Watch the playlist(Updated)
http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL489ED89FA4490878&feature=plcp


Difficulty: Hard
Stage Name Player's Character 
Yellow Turbans Rebellion (part 1) Liu Bei
Yellow Turbans Rebellion (part 2) Liu Bei


The Yellow Turban Rebellion (黄巾の乱), sometimes also translated as the Yellow Scarves Rebellion, was a peasant rebellion led by Zhang Jiao against Emperor Ling of the Han Dynasty. It is named for the color of the scarves which the rebels wore around their heads. The rebels were associated with secret Taiping Taoist societies and the rebellion marked an important point in the history of Taoism. The rebellion is the opening event in the Chinese literary classic, Romance of the Three Kingdoms.


This one's special, it has ENBseries mods and FXAA tool.

Ultra Settings.
Watch in 720p or 1080p
